    <div xml:id="PN387-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. cēramāṉ cikkaṟpaḷḷittuñciya celvakkaṭuṅkōvāḻiyātaṉaik kuṇṭukaṭpāliyātaṉ.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
